posting_body: ['This building is located on 8th Street SE where it meets Hennepin Ave.', 'Super easy to get to campus, close to a bus stop.', 'It is a large garden level 2 bedroom.', 'Huge Livingroom.', 'Pass though kitchen with space for a kitchen table.', '2 good sized bedrooms with large closets.', 'Plenty of windows for natural light, it is a corner unit so extra windows in the bedrooms.', 'Built in AC', 'Rent is $1250', 'Heat, water and trash are all included', 'Parking is $65 ( FREE TO YOU)', 'Give IrvingProperties a call or email to set up a showing.', 'show contact info', '.', 'We are looking for a September 1st or 15th move in.', ' I can be a little flexible.', '****1/2 OFF 1 months rent with qualifying credit and year lease******', 'This is a no pet and no smoking building.', 'Photos and video are of a similiar unit on the garden level, same size and shape.', 'https://youtu.be/4DcMlDNIUOs']
